OL,3,CLyndon Farnham to stay on as Jersey's
OL,4,CChief Minister
OL,6,FIncumbent Lyndon Farnham will remain
OL,7,Fas Jersey's Chief Minister after he
OL,8,Fwas the only candidate to put himself
OL,9,Fforward for the top job.
OL,11,FPoll-topper Helen Miles had been
OL,12,Fexpected to challenge him, but instead
OL,13,Fnominated fellow Senator-elect Farnham
OL,14,Ffor leader following "positive and
OL,15,Fconstructive discussions" between them.
OL,17,FThe current Chief Minister had made it
OL,18,Fclear throughout his election campaign
OL,19,Fthat he would like to continue in the
OL,20,Frole.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
