PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1781453487
OL,3,CLyndon Farnham to stay on as Jersey's
OL,4,CChief Minister
OL,6,FHe strengthened his chances with a
OL,7,Fstrong election result, emerging as
OL,8,Fthe third most popular candidate for
OL,9,FSenator.
OL,11,FDr Miles has previously served as the
OL,12,FJustice and Home Affairs Minister and
OL,13,Fwants to continue in that position, a
OL,14,Fmove backed by Mr Farnham, according
OL,15,Fto a joint statement released by the
OL,16,Fpair.
OL,18,FShe states that "several islanders and
OL,19,FStates Members have asked me to put my
OL,20,Fname forward for Chief Minister."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1781453487
OL,3,CLyndon Farnham to stay on as Jersey's
OL,4,CChief Minister
OL,6,FDespite that, Dr Miles says that she
OL,7,Fhas come to a "mutual agreement" with
OL,8,FMr Farnham, recognising his "strong
OL,9,Flevel of support within the Assembly"
OL,10,Fand is opting not to stand to avoid a
OL,11,F"divisive and unnecessary contest".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
