OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1781453487
OL,3,CLyndon Farnham to stay on as Jersey's
OL,4,CChief Minister
OL,6,FThey both add: "Our shared objective
OL,7,Fhas been to bring unity and stability
OL,8,Fto Jersey, and to ensure that
OL,9,Fattention can shift as quickly as
OL,10,Fpossible to addressing the key issues
OL,11,Fraised by islanders during the
OL,12,Felection - delivering economic growth,
OL,13,Fmaking Jersey more affordable,
OL,14,Fstrengthening discipline in public
OL,15,Ffinances, and improving public
OL,16,Fservices."
OL,18,FMr Farnham has served as Chief
OL,19,FMinister since 2024, following a vote
OL,20,Fof no-confidence in his predecessor,
OL,21,FKristina Moore.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1781453487
OL,3,CLyndon Farnham to stay on as Jersey's
OL,4,CChief Minister
OL,6,FWith no one challenging him, no vote
OL,7,Fis needed and Mr Farnham will be re-
OL,8,Felected to the island's top political
OL,9,Fposition.
OL,11,FHowever, he will still make a
OL,12,Fstatement and face an hour of
OL,13,Fquestioning in the States Chamber on
OL,14,FFriday 19 June.
OL,16,FMinisters will be selected by States
OL,17,FMembers on Friday 26 June, with Mr
OL,18,FFarnham proposing his choices before
OL,19,Fan Assembly vote, where other
OL,20,Fcandidates can also nominate
OL,21,Fthemselves.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1781453487
OL,3,CLyndon Farnham to stay on as Jersey's
OL,4,CChief Minister
OL,6,FOnce all the ministerial roles are
OL,7,Fdecided, they will be formally
OL,8,Fappointed on Monday 29 June.
OL,10,FMr Farnham says: "I thank Helen for
OL,11,Fher positive approach to our
OL,12,Fdiscussions this week and look forward
OL,13,Fto welcoming her back into the
OL,14,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1781453487
OL,3,CLyndon Farnham to stay on as Jersey's
OL,4,CChief Minister
OL,6,F"We will be working closely together,
OL,7,Fas well as with the new Council of
OL,8,FMinisters and the wider States
OL,9,FAssembly, to continue to make progress
OL,10,Fon the issues that matter most to
OL,11,Fislanders and to build confidence in
OL,12,FJersey's future."
OL,14,FThe required eight elected States
OL,15,FMembers who put their names behind Mr
OL,16,FFarnham's nomination were Alan
OL,17,FMaclean, Mary Le Hegarat, Mark Boleat,
OL,18,FHelen Miles, Arlene Maltman, Malcolm
OL,19,FFerey, Richard Honeycombe and Mark
OL,20,FLabey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
